</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>BMW i7 電動車秘密抵港，配按摩椅及 8K 全景屏幕</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/06/bmw-i7/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=bmw-i7</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 06 May 2022 09:01:31 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[bmw]]></category><category><![CDATA[BMW i7]]></category><category><![CDATA[i7]]></category><category><![CDATA[idrive]]></category><category><![CDATA[iX]]></category><category><![CDATA[xdrive]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1098672</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>BMW 香港剛剛為首款電動豪華旗艦房車 BMW i7 xDrive 60 在香港舉行閉門的傳媒預覽會，續航力達 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>BMW 香港剛剛為首款電動豪華旗艦房車 BMW i7 xDrive 60 在香港舉行閉門的傳媒預覽會，續航力達 590-625KM（WLTP）的 i7 除了擁有極之豪華及科幻的外形設計，後座更配備懸浮式影院屏幕，31.3 吋 8k 32:9 比例全景顯示器，全車內外滿載科技元素，BMW i7 xDrive 60 的「一換一」意向價約為港幣 200 萬！</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098680 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120401-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120401-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120401-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120401-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120401-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120401-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120401-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120704-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120704-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120704-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120704-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120704-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120704-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120704-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_120704-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>BMW i7 xDrive 60 搭載 101.7kWh 鋰電池及前後雙馬達設計，最大馬力可達 544ps 及 76kgm 扭力，0 至 100km/h 只需 4.7 秒，而且續航力長達 590-625KM（WLTP），而其全新的 BMW Individual 服務，可供車主按喜好為車身外觀選擇 Two Tone 兩種顏色，分別為車身窗框、車頭蓋、車頂、車尾頂的主色，及車門柄以下的副色，令車輛更能展現獨特個性。i7 車身體積比上一代更長，尺寸為 5,391 X 1,950 X 1,544mm，前後軸距達 3,215mm，後座更加寬敞，加上配備按摩椅及比 iX 更強勁的 Bowers &amp; Wilkins 4D Surround 劇院音響系統，娛樂性及舒適度令人耳目一新!</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121006-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121006-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121006-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121006-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121006-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121006-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121006-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121006-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121925-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1098697 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads