/20220505_121425-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121445-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121445-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121445-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121445-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121445-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121445-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121445-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121445-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121653-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098690" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121653-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121653-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121653-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121653-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121653-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121653-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220505_121653-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>BMW 7 將同時提供 i7 電動版及 740Li Mild-Hybrid 版本選擇。</p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
